data.mdl_comment: The module for the Simplciité Training platform

data.sys_desc:
Examples :
Simple usecase ---------------------------
Editing through UI, using Simplicité indexing
```json { "edition_type": "UI", "index_type": "simplicite" } ```
Advanced usecase ---------------------------
Editing through Filesystem (possible git repo), using ElasticSearch indexing
```json { "edition_type": "FILESYSTEM", "filesystem_contentdir": "/path/to/directory/to/sync/with", "index_type": "elasticsearch", "esi_config": { "instance": "https://elasticsearchinstance.mydomain.not", "index": "docs_myinstance", "credentials":"user:password" } } ```

data.grp_comment: The group for the administrators of the training platform

data.lov_value: Administration of content for this isntance is made through synchronization with a filesystem directory (usually a git repository) hosting the content, no UI changes are allowed for this object.
